title: United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Rubber & Related Articles
description: Imports of Intra EU - Rubber & Related Articles in the United Kingdom increased to 180.05 GBP Million in September from 174.89 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Intra EU - Rubber & Related Articles in the United Kingdom averaged 142.86 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 258.45 GBP Million in January of 2022 and a record low of 62.74 GBP Million in December of 2001. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Rubber & Related Articles.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
